Fit in Chelsea: Binky Felstead, Spencer Matthews, Ollie Proudlock and Lucy Watson have joined forces with the UK's top trainers to create their very own fitness DVD. MIC: FIT

The DVD, which lands on December 1, promises to reveal the cast members' secrets to 'looking hot with a hectic lifestyle and how they keep fit when not partying in Chelsea'.

'Featuring the hottest fitness trends with four fun, high-energy 20-minute workouts that will have you looking toned for the King's Road, MIC:FIT is perfect to fit into your busy schedule: it gets results and will help keep you looking and feeling amazing during the festive season and beyond,' reads the description.

