Despite Lucy’s claims she’s biologically incapable of sweating, she proves otherwise with her Beach Body Workout that uses just bodyweight without any equipment. 

It focuses on getting all the right bits toned before you put on that bikini or beachwear - something the actress-turned-model knows all about.

And then there's hipster Proudlock, who introduces a special yoga and Pilates-inspired workout called the Chelsea Morning Power Stretch. It not only works on your core but also helps with your recovery from the more strenuous routines, he assures. 

The Chelsea clan are currently filming for the latest series, which - quite fittingly - sees Binky dating a personal trainer, Proudlock rocking crucifix earrings, Spencer living up to his lothario status and Lucy getting up in everyone's grill.

